Exp No: 19 Name of Experiment : Session Handling Using PHP 
Aim: Write a PHP program to implement a cookie and session based counter. 
• Create Cookies variable using PHP 
• Create a session variable using PHP 
• Display the session variable using PHP 
• Display the cookies variable using PHP 

INPUT :
<?php

session_start();


ini_set('session.gc_maxlifetime', 5);


if (isset($_SESSION['session_counter'])) {
    $_SESSION['session_counter'] += 1;
} else {
    $_SESSION['session_counter'] = 1;
}


if (isset($_COOKIE['cookie_counter'])) {
    $cookie_counter = $_COOKIE['cookie_counter'] + 1;
} else {
    $cookie_counter = 1;
}
setcookie("cookie_counter", $cookie_counter, time() + (86400 * 30)); // Cookie lasts for 30 days
?>

